---
/**
 * Dismissable cookie consent banner, fixed bottom. Uses localStorage to
 * remember user choice. Defaults to shown on first visit.
 */
---

<div
  data-cookie-consent
  role="dialog"
  aria-label="Pemberitahuan cookie"
  class="fixed bottom-0 inset-x-0 z-50 p-4 pointer-events-none"
>
  <div class="container-wide">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-surface p-5 lg:p-6 flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto translate-y-full opacity-0 transition-all duration-500 pointer-events-auto">
      <span class="i-carbon-cookie text-3xl text-accent shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted flex-1">
        Kami menggunakan cookie untuk meningkatkan pengalaman Anda. Dengan melanjutkan, Anda menyetujui
        <a href="/kebijakan-privasi" class="text-primary hover:underline">Kebijakan Privasi</a> kami.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 shrink-0">
        <button
          type="button"
          data-cookie-reject
          class="h-10 px-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium text-ink-muted hover:text-ink hover:bg-surface transition-colors"
        >Tolak</button>
        <button
          type="button"
          data-cookie-accept
          class="h-10 px-5 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors"
        >Terima</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
